data.description: Welcome to this pristine 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home on Dataw Island. 468 BB Sams boasts a fresh and updated feel and offers one level living with stunning views of the Morgan River Course's 17th fairway. The remodeled kitchen features high-quality finishes and modern appliances. One of the highlights of the property is the screened-in porch and rear patio. It is perfect for relaxing, entertaining, or dining al fresco. Being on Dataw Island offers a lifestyle unlike any other, with access to world class amenities, a vibrant community, and the beauty of South Carolina's stunning coastal landscapes. The best of Lowcountry living.
